{
  "texts": [
    "To select algorithms, we use the same criteria as the bake off.",
    "Firstly, the algorithm must have been published post bake off in a high quality conference or journal (or be an extension of such an algorithm).",
    "Secondly, it must have been evaluated on one of the UCR/UEA dataset releases, or on a subset thereof, with reasoning provided for any datasets that are missing.",
    "Thirdly, source code must be available and easily adaptable to the time series machine learning tools we use (i.e.",
    "usable or easily wrappable in a Java or Python environment)."
  ]
}